txt.en: Shakal-atrâd can be found in central Elderslade.\n\nYou should defeat enemies within the ruins of Shakal-atrâd.
Shakal-atrâd can be found in central Elderslade.\n\nYou should defeat enemies within the ruins of Shakal-atrâd.

The old dwarf-ruins of Shakal-atrâd have been defiled by the forces of Gundabad for many years. Inside gathers a party of Angmarim ritualists who have converted the old watch-tower into an evil ritual shrine. The Angmarim must be defeated, and quickly.
The old dwarf-ruins of Shakal-atrâd have been defiled by Gundabad forces for many years.
You have defeated many of the Angmarim who reside in the ruins of Shakal-atrâd. The dwarves in Elderslade will be grateful for your efforts on this day.
